of determination, choice, regeneration, pride and hope, 2024 will be a French vintage.\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 886, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 871, \"end\": 877, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.999955804141205, \"rank\": 4.419730624365633e-05, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My dear compatriots\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 793}, {\"ngram\": \"Year\", \"from\": 795, \"to\": 799}, {\"ngram\": \"determination\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 816}, {\"ngram\": \"choice\", \"from\": 818, \"to\": 824}, {\"ngram\": \"regeneration\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 838}, {\"ngram\": \"pride\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 845}, {\"ngram\": \"hope\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 854}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I wish you a beautiful and happy new year.\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 929, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Long live the Republic, long live France!\\\"\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 972, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Republic\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 952}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Macron posted on X (formerly Twitter).\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 1011, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 973, \"end\": 979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.887813251088696e-32, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"X\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 991}, {\"ngram\": \"formerly Twitter\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1009}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mes chers compatriotes,Ann\\u00e9e de d\\u00e9termination, de choix, de r\\u00e9g\\u00e9n\\u00e9ration, de fiert\\u00e9 et d'esp\\u00e9rance, 2024 sera un mill\\u00e9sime fran\\u00e7ais.Je vous souhaite une belle et heureuse ann\\u00e9e.Vive la R\\u00e9publique, vive la France !pic.twitter.com/9DkHAwBr3M Paris, along with other major countries like Australia, New Zealand, the UAE, Berlin, and Taiwan, ring in 2024 on Monday.Taiwan welcomed the New Year with fireworks.Meanwhile, huge fireworks displays were used to celebrate the beginning of the new year in Greece, Germany, and France.However, because of a number of ongoing conflicts, such as Russia's invasion of Ukraine and the Israel-Hamas war, celebrations are likely going to be subdued in several parts of the globe.Over a million people celebrated the New Year on Sunday night amid stunning fireworks displays, illuminating the skies over Australia's Sydney Harbour and New Zealand's tallest structure, the Sky Tower in Auckland.The countdown commenced against an illuminated digital display near the top of the 328-metre (1,076-foot) communications and observation tower, Al Jazeera reported.As the clock struck midnight in Australia's largest city, Sydney, a 12-minute fireworks display erupted around the Sydney Harbour Bridge.The small Pacific island nations of Tonga, Samoa and Kiribati had ushered in the New Year an hour earlier.\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 2347, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1299, \"end\": 1308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9978974056133494, \"rank\": 0.0021069503530593446, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 1310, \"end\": 1321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealanders\", \"score\": 0.9439767290718108, \"rank\": 0.029225087842713247, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealanders\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealanders\"}, {\"begin\": 1327, \"end\": 1330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Arab_Emirates\", \"score\": 0.99